name: Maternity
description:
The beauty of a woman is one thing but during the time that she is carrying her unborn child is a miraculous sight.  One that deserves to be captured.  Come share a shoot with me.  Have your hair and makeup professionally done by our team and let me capture that amazing baby bump. 

-remember no products are included in the session fee

name: High School Seniors and Teens
description:
Our team prides itself on doing age appropriate posing and hair and makeup.  Everything is approved by mom!  

Speaking of mom...Hey Mom!  Ever wanted to have a few images with your teen or high school senior?  We want you to have a great time too!  While your teen or senior is doing their shoot you can be getting your hair and makeup done as well.  We will save a few minutes at the end of their session so you may sneak in and we will snap a few photos!  It is important to have these images to cherish for a lifetime.  Soon they will be off to college and you can look back on your session and be glad you were able to share in the experience with them. 

-remember product is not included in the session fee

name: Session Fee-Family
description:
Family sessions are so much fun but they can be very stressful.  Let me guide you through the entire process to take the guesswork out of capturing your family memories.  From wardrobe to products I help you with your toughest decisions that arise when getting ready for your session.  Usually the glue to the family is mom so here at Ashley Torchia Photography we know how important it is for mom to be happy.  Mom will receive full hair and makeup by our professional staff so you look your very best for your photos.  If there are little/teen girls in the family who would also like to have their hair styled by our staff that is also welcomed.  Talk about a girls day!


-remember no product is included in the session fee-only the time and talent of the photographer and staff before and during the session itself.  You will receive a full price list upon request at ashleytorchiaphotography@hotmail.com

name: Gift Certificate | Start at $150
description:
Give the best gift you can give this holiday season.  Every session includes professional hair and makeup so you can be rest assured your loved ones will look and feel gorgeous.  Send the gift of love this year.  They deserve it!

You may purchase just a session fee or a session fee and then some!  Whether you want to pick out product or gift them credit so they may choose there is a plan to meet your every need.

Folio Boxes Explained:  Folio Boxes are the ultimate keepsake item.  You may choose from an 11x14  sleek black or luxurious linen  keepsake box.  Inside all photos will be 7x10 and matted at 11x14 so they are ready to frame or keep tucked away for safe keeping.  The box comes with 6, 10 or 20 images inside.  You choose which is best for you!  Each image chosen comes loaded on a USB in digital form so you may share with friends and family.  Extra images are available for purchase.

name: Portrait Box | Start at $950
description: I am in LOVE with this new product!  I am so happy to introduce the Portrait Box.  The Portrait Box is an 11x14 box that can be purchased in charcoal black or luxurious linen.  The box serves as an elegant cover to the images from your session.  Each image is sized to 7x10 and is matted (total size 11x14) so you may preserve your image in the box as a keepsake or you can take it out of the box and it comes ready to be framed!  Images come in sets of 6, 10, or 20 (small, medium & large).  More images can be purchased at any time.  This box is THE new album!  The BIG difference is you can keep all of your images in one place like an album but if you ever want your photo out on display for all to enjoy-now you can!

name: Prints | Start at $200
description: Prints are all matted and mounted and ready to be framed! Any print(s) purchased includes the high resolution digital version on USB
